  "remarks": "Elena Shapurova is the Russian-appointed “Minister of the Ministry of Education and Science of Zaporizhia region”. She enacted re-education policies of Ukrainian children in the Russian-occupied region of Zaporizhzhia, diminishing Ukrainian-language classes and increasing the number of Russian classes, including promoting Russian culture and\ncivic-education classes. Therefore, she is supporting and implementing actions and policies which undermine and threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty, and independence of Ukraine.",
